pullRequest.title: The enforcer rule to pass repositories for artifact resolutions

commit.message:
Preparing test for #1609.

This fails because the BOM project cannot find the
artifact.

RepositorySystemSession does not seem to remember
repositories.

commit.message:
No need to pass MavenProject

DependencyGraphBuilder can take list of repository URLs
so that it uses them when building graphs.
